&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-markdown" data-lang="markdown">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">![&lt;span class="nt">图片 1&lt;/span>](&lt;span class="na">1.jpg&lt;/span>) ![&lt;span class="nt">图片 2&lt;/span>](&lt;span class="na">2.jpg&lt;/span>)
